Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:03.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:06.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to stop the out-of-control Laxus,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:09.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, and even Mystogan, \Nchallenged him in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:12.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But after an unexpected turn of events,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:15.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza headed to destroy the \NThunder Palace on her own,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:19.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,while Natsu and Laxus began a confrontation \Nwith the guild on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:42.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo Ho! Steer that rudder! Hard to port!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:45.92,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo Ho! Our high-flyin' lives are every which way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:58.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When the sun goes down, there's a bon voyage bash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:04.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't sad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:11.35,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're alive, we'll meet again somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:15.64,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast straight through a headwind, set off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:20.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay strong until the tears dry up! A man gotta be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:25.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, friends, laugh one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:29.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof of our strong, strong bonds!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:37.77,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, grab that map to the shining future!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:04.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:05.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:09.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Triple Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:23.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,198...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:29.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,199...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:41.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to destroy them all \Nat once, I still need more...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:49.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already out of magical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm also out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:01.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not even three minutes \Nuntil the Thunder Palace activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:04.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:07.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't nothing... gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:12.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:35.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I have another 100 blades...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... simultaneously...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can everyone hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:53.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:55.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look up at the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:58.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:00.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:04.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up you lazy bums!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:08.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:14.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if there's anyone still \Nfighting, hold up for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a voice in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Warren's telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He can speak directly into people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:26.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:30.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta destroy those things floating in \Nthe sky with all the magic power we got!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:33.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic spell from Laxus \Nthat'll attack the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:37.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are Laxus's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:46.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren, why do you know \Nabout the Thunder Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:48.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice... Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:49.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:54.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Took me a while to find the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:00.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza? You're not turned to stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if Erza's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:07.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...are the others? Is Levy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:08.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is also okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:15.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So is Bisca, Alzack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:21.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness... Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My telepathy can't reach \Nall the way to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to do it with \Nthe people who can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy those things up in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:31.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Warren!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget what you did to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Max?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:41.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was, like, really trying to \Nsave Erza and the others, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Droy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Alzack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that's gonna cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:51.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You hit me with a sneak attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:55.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna forgive you, Laki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:09.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Save the fightin' for later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no time now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the things floating in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:21.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I don't hold back, I'm way stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:23.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You always attack first, think later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds more like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:40.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:43.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the city are in real danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:47.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to all work together to \Nprotect the city of Magnolia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:51.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we combine our powers, \Nwe can overcome anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:55.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've learned after coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I just joined Fairy Tail recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:05.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But my feelings for this guild \Nare as strong as anybody's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:10.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail has been my \Ndream since long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all work together...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:22.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's protect our guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and our city!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that won't convince you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:39.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy all the lacrima myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:51.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:55.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really gonna let the \Nnewbie one up you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not new any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got more Fairy Tail \Nspirit than any of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, you're exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll settle things later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:08.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't argue with that, now can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:10.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I'm thinking straight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:14.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all you folks ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:18.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:28.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren, we'll settle this after \Nthose things are destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:30.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makao, you can't handle this! Take a nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:32.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:34.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure prance around a lot for an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They have Body Link magic protecting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:42.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you attack them, you'll \Nget damaged yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:43.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it hurts, I'll do it anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I always looked up to Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've gotten to be such \Ngood friends with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, a lot of things have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone has always been so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:58.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guild is where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:03.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart yells out "This \Nis where I should be!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:07.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:12.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it was Fairy Tail \Nthat made me strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:15.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:18.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:25.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle the 200 to the north!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you destroy all \Nthe ones around the south!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave a single one left!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:34.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:48.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forth, my blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:59.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Max Speed Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:16.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:22.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail just keeps doing things \Nflashier and flashier each year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:16.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:23.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Birds of a feather, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:31.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We really are a great guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:34.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'd be even better if Laxus \Ngot over this rebellious phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:36.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alzack, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:40.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Droy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:42.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:47.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of this guild needs to be changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:50.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all in the same circle of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:57.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You never even tried to join that circle! \NHow're you gonna become the master, Laxus?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:11.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I going to become the master, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By force!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:20.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:26.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The master... Your grandfather... \NHe's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:44.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about enough, Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:49.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail will never be yours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:51.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:56.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Trying to force a \Nbargain was pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:13:00.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have relied on my \Nown power from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:06.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This overwhelming power is my very identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:11.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So when I beat that power, \Nyou'll finally give in, Laxus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:16.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:28.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll devour you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:58.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He really is strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:04.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Resound, my summoned thunder's boom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:11.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall from the heavens and turn all to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Raging Bolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:29.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the strongest in the guild again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:39.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry. You can't answer \Nbecause you've been turned to dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you his ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:49.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with you \Nbeing happy he's wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:52.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he ain't been.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:55.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gettin' rid of him is my role.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:00.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Another snack shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear, disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:09.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who stands in my \Nway should just disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a personal grudge with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:20.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His monstrous strength \Nis the real deal though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got Makarov's blood running in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:28.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it, but we've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:34.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna defeat Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, how could I ever team up with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:37.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:41.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Laxus you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear! Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an enemy of the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:54.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop him here \Nto protect the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:58.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of them are down for the count \Nafter the counterattack from the Thunder Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:02.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what will happen \Nif we don't stop him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna protect the guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:11.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether I protect the guild or \Ndestroy the guild, it's my choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:15.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say that there wasn't room \Nenough in the sky for two dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:20.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But with all this annoying lightning, \Nyou can't fly in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:24.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but I'm only teaming \Nup this once, Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:28.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll settle things one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:29.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:46.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:50.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pillar of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:06.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brilliant Blaze of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:14.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spears of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Poles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:20.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:40.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the power of you working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:44.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked you can call \Nyourselves Dragon Slayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:47.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we damage him at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:53.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how strong he is, after being \Nhit with all that Dragon Slayer magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:58.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's simple really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:03.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the old man's lectures, \Nso I kept it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:06.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll show you special.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:24.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:26.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also a Dragon Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:29.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Thunder Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay down already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:18:59.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all numb...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:05.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, Erza, Mystogan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:08.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the old man, the trash in the guild,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:11.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,all the people in Magnolia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:16.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make them all disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:21.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this crazy magical power?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This power... It's Gramps's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:30.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It targets everything the \Ncaster sees as an enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:33.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Makarov's Ultimate Spell of Judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:41.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:48.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The spell that destroyed \NMaster Joze in one hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:50.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:06.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:07.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:08.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:10.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:11.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The master is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:18.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The master... Your grandfather is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...on death's door!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:27.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:39.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On death's door? Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:58.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:03.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my chance of becoming \Nmaster just went back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:15.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear, Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll build it up again from scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't lose to anyone! Everyone will \Ncower in fear before my ultimate guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:30.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:32.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:36.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Law is invoked!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:23.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That time we laughed, saying "we're both like each other,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:33.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,we even kindly overlooked the little lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:39.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose a place to go back to together, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:48.72,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'll protect that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:53.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The meetings and partings numerous as the stars in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.16,0:22:55.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,All the things I don't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.61,0:23:00.29,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I feel like I don't need any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:05.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to see you by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:11.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,all my happiness and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:13.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:16.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start our tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:20.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it like we've just been reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:26.20,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Like flowers blown in a summer wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:34.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,let us bloom brightly in this instant.
